            <h3 class="media-heading">Trimming Tips</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Some people like perfectly manicured hedges and others just trim them right before they start to look unwieldy. It is a matter of your preference.  This yard service is only needed a couple of times per year.</li>
                <li>The frequency at which you need to trim hedges depends on the hedge type. It also depends on the age of the hedge.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

